\frametitle{Some PDEs}

{\blue Advection Equation (constant-coefficient $u$, 1D in space):}

\[
q_t + uq_x = 0 \quad\text{for}~ t\geq 0,
\]
with initial data $q(x,0) = \ico q(x)$ (for Cauchy problem)

\vsp
{\blue Exact solution:} $q(x,t) = \ico q(x-ut, 0)$

